data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.100 set value "Careful where you step—some vines bite back."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.101 set value "The canopy watches, always. It has more eyes than you think."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.102 set value "A Patron stalks the ravine below—glowing purple, name and all."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.103 set value "Parrots hear more than they repeat."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.104 set value "The temple crates refill themselves. Ancient magic, older than us."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.105 set value "The ocelots know things we have forgotten."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.106 set value "I swear that vine moved on its own."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.107 set value "A Furia tore through here last night—nameless, howling chaos."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.108 set value "You smell like you have been inside a dungeon."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.109 set value "The Guidestone near the falls still hums with old power."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.110 set value "We lose more golems to moss than monsters."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.111 set value "Someone found Mjolnir buried in the temple roots. It sang to them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.112 set value "That mossy stone was not cracked yesterday."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.113 set value "Never dig near the roots—they scream."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.114 set value "Dream Surges make the canopy glow violet. Beautiful and terrible."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.115 set value "The monkeys do not show themselves to outsiders."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.116 set value "You brought cocoa? Now you can stay."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.117 set value "An Exquisite Patron lives in the deep growth—pink glow, cold eyes."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.118 set value "Do not eat anything purple in the jungle."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.119 set value "Thunder sounds different under thick leaves."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.120 set value "The Expeditionist who camped here said the crates reset faster for her."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.121 set value "We follow parrots, not compasses."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.122 set value "If it glows green, walk away slowly."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.123 set value "The Ruin Watch ticks loudest near old temples. I can hear it now."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.124 set value "Do not whistle near the stone faces."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.125 set value "Some trees are older than time itself."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.126 set value "A Greater Furia came through—three stars of pure disorder."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.127 set value "You ever been chased by your own shadow?"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.128 set value "That is not mud—it is memory."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.129 set value "The Companion Catalogue lists jungle parrots. They bond deeply here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.130 set value "Bring melons, not questions."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.131 set value "The jungle chooses who gets out."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.132 set value "A Bartender once brewed something from these vines. Nobody slept right after."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.133 set value "Watch the water—some of it is eyes."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.134 set value "I saw an Enderman climb a vine."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.135 set value "Stormcaller was pulled from a lightning-struck tree. The tree still burns."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.136 set value "You hear a flute? That is not us."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.137 set value "The jungle grows over lies and truths alike."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.138 set value "Our cats disappear for days and come back glowing."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.139 set value "Your Dream Rate feels higher here. The jungle amplifies it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.140 set value "Creepers here do not hiss—they whisper."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.141 set value "The Codex speaks of things buried beneath these roots."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.142 set value "I traded emeralds for silence once."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.143 set value "We do not ring bells—we shake leaves."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.144 set value "A Mythical Patron with a gold glow was sighted near the gorge."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.145 set value "I saw a witch walk through a wall of vines."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.146 set value "The jungle heals itself, but not us."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.147 set value "The Advantage Tree has branches even the jungle envies."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.148 set value "That stone block was not there yesterday."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.149 set value "We grow what we cannot explain."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.150 set value "Do not wear gold near the sacred grove."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.151 set value "Earthshaker split the temple floor in half. The crack still grows."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.152 set value "The temple does not like loud footsteps."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.153 set value "Every ruin has a purpose, even the broken ones."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.154 set value "A Wandering Trader vanished near the old shrine. His llamas stayed."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.155 set value "That is not a pond—it is breathing."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.156 set value "You lost your compass? Good. The jungle prefers it that way."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.157 set value "The Nymph profession fits these woods—they speak to living things."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.158 set value "Redstone does not work right out here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.159 set value "Do not bring jungle saplings into the Nether."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.160 set value "Harmonized blessings feel stronger under the canopy."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.161 set value "If you dig at night, dig fast."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.162 set value "A parrot once told me my future. I did not like it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.163 set value "The oldest vines grow over unmarked graves."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.164 set value "A Minor Furia circled the village—just one star, but enough."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.165 set value "The temple door only opens to silence."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.166 set value "Our golem left. Said he was called somewhere deeper."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.167 set value "Mob Heads hang from the temple walls. Trophies or warnings."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.168 set value "You are not lost. The jungle just moved."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.169 set value "That is not a monkey. That is something else entirely."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.170 set value "Pebble of Dreams was found in a hollow log. Still warm."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.171 set value "We do not grow wheat—we grow warnings."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.172 set value "That was not lightning. That was something worse."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.173 set value "A Rare Patron with aqua markings guards the western temple."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.174 set value "I traded my bed for peace of mind."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.175 set value "If the parrots leave, so should you."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.176 set value "Windrunner boots left prints on the canopy tops. Impossible, yet there."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.177 set value "Our well is deep enough to find echoes."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.178 set value "You are breathing loud enough to wake the ruins."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.179 set value "The Tomb system preserves the fallen. Even the jungle respects that."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.180 set value "Do not mine too long under the old temple."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.181 set value "We measure time by tree rings, not clocks."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.182 set value "Dragon Boots leave scorch marks on wet leaves. Seen them myself."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.183 set value "That tree ate our last cartographer."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.184 set value "Do not laugh at the idol. It notices."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.185 set value "The Hunter profession thrives here—so much prey, so much danger."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.186 set value "If you see fog, do not move."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.187 set value "We do not plant—things grow on their own."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.188 set value "I once met a skeleton wearing an Uncommon blue glow. Named itself."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.189 set value "Do not let the vines touch your tools."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.190 set value "You built with jungle wood? Brave."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.191 set value "That crate was full an hour ago. The magic cycles, I think."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.192 set value "When it rains green, stay inside."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.193 set value "Weapon Mastery counts for something against what lurks here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.194 set value "We never say the witch's name aloud."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.195 set value "That emerald is humming. Can you not hear it?"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.196 set value "Venomfang Crossbow was crafted from a jungle spider's fang. Fitting."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.197 set value "The trees bend when no one is watching."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.198 set value "We lose more traders than we gain."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.199 set value "That bridge only appears at sunset. Old magic, not redstone."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.200 set value "Did the vines just move toward you?"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.201 set value "Parrots do not lie, but they do not help either."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.202 set value "An Artificer traveled here seeking resonance from the temple stones."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.203 set value "Do not step near the hollow logs."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.204 set value "That drumbeat is not coming from us."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.205 set value "Blaze Core pulses with heat. Wrong element for a jungle, yet here it rests."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.206 set value "Do not look directly at the stone heads."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.207 set value "My cousin lives in a tree now. Says the spinosaurs keep him safe."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.208 set value "That totem was not carved—it grew."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.209 set value "There is a sound only the trees can hear."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.210 set value "The sky turned violet last week. A Dream Surge. Crates appeared overnight."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.211 set value "You smell like Nether ash."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.212 set value "The parrots do not mimic—they record."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.213 set value "A Common Patron with a gray glow lurks by the river. Barely a threat."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.214 set value "You dream of vines yet? The jungle sends those."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.215 set value "That compass spins for a reason near Guidestones."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.216 set value "We do not have roads—just regrets."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.217 set value "A Wise Wanderer passed through. Said the roots remember everything."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.218 set value "That golem left footprints going upward."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.219 set value "You ever see moss blink? I have."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.220 set value "Heartstone resonates deepest where life is thickest. Like here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.221 set value "The old bell rings when it wants to."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.222 set value "Our moss grows from memory."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.223 set value "If it glows, it is claimed—by Patron or by jungle."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.224 set value "That Wandering Trader never came back."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.225 set value "We do not prune—we apologize to the vines."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.226 set value "The Deku Shield was found wrapped in living roots. Still growing."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.227 set value "The ruins breathe deeper after midnight."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.228 set value "Do not let the parrots follow you home."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.229 set value "I do not trade after dusk—not anymore."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.230 set value "The jungle hates redstone. Prefers older magic."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.231 set value "You stepped on sacred roots. Best apologize."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.232 set value "An Ornate Patron stands in the temple clearing—purple glow, ancient name."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.233 set value "That idol's eyes follow travelers."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.234 set value "Do not eat anything you did not plant yourself."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.235 set value "Retired Adventurers come to the jungle to forget. The jungle remembers for them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.236 set value "I once caught a fish that whispered my name."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.237 set value "The witch trades in names and memories."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.238 set value "Structure Crates in the temple refill. Patience rewards the faithful."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.239 set value "You build fast—but the vines build faster."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.240 set value "That axe is too loud for this place."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.241 set value "I heard the jungle speak. It said a name I will not repeat."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.242 set value "A Beekeeper tried to set up hives here. The jungle disagreed."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.243 set value "The ruins were not always ruined."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.244 set value "We lost a farmer to a tree once."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.245 set value "Your tools will not help you here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.246 set value "Dreams come thicker under the canopy. Your Dream Rate knows."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.247 set value "The vines grow better with rain. And with fear."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.248 set value "Some trees are older than the moon above them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.249 set value "You feel that? The ground is listening."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.250 set value "A Miner came for ore. The jungle gave him roots instead."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.251 set value "The jungle always reclaims what it lends."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.252 set value "You bring silence? Good. The jungle rewards that."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.253 set value "Do not trust that glowing flower. Could be a Furia lure."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.254 set value "If it is mossy, it is probably watching."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.255 set value "The parrots fly in circles when danger comes."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.256 set value "Stay out of the green fog. Something hunts inside it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.257 set value "A Zookeeper tried taming the ocelots. They tamed her instead."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.258 set value "The sun does not shine here the same way."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.259 set value "I heard a laugh come from deep inside the vines."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.260 set value "During a Dream Surge the boundaries thin. Things slip through."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.261 set value "That vine has moved again since we started talking."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.262 set value "Do not say your name near the shrine."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.263 set value "The parrots told me you would come."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.264 set value "An ocelot companion is worth more than iron armor here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.265 set value "We do not keep track of how many live here anymore."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.266 set value "The temple door opens on its own when the crate is ready."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.267 set value "We all have stories. The jungle has more than all of us."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.268 set value "Your footsteps are too loud for sacred ground."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.269 set value "I once saw obsidian weep in the rain."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.270 set value "You cannot escape the roots. They know where you sleep."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.271 set value "Trade quickly—something with a name is watching."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.272 set value "Do not speak of the jungle in the Nether. It hears you there too."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.273 set value "That is not fog—it is spores from something ancient."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.274 set value "You blinked. The vines moved closer."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.275 set value "I saw an eye open on a tree once. Just one. Enough."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.276 set value "The parrots keep flying west toward the Guidestone."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.277 set value "Some ruins do not want to be found. They hide themselves."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.278 set value "You better hope that was not sacred."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.279 set value "That sound? Not thunder. Earthshaker, maybe."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.280 set value "We do not use doors—we use warnings."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.281 set value "Watch your back near the hollow trees."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.282 set value "I do not trust anyone who walks in a straight line here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.283 set value "Do not point at the stone face. It takes offense."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.284 set value "You came alone? Bold. Or foolish."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.285 set value "The jungle accepts, but it never forgets a trespass."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.286 set value "Do not rest beneath twisted roots. Dreams get trapped there."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.287 set value "That humming is not music. It is the temple resonating."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.288 set value "You should leave before the rain comes."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.289 set value "The jungle likes you—for now."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.290 set value "Do not eat the purple mushrooms."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.291 set value "The parrots stopped talking. Something with a glow is near."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.292 set value "You feel heavier here, do you not? The canopy presses down."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.293 set value "That sound means the temple is waking. The crate stirs."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.294 set value "The vines are listening to every word we share."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.295 set value "You brought gifts, right? The jungle expects tribute."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.296 set value "The canopy saw what you did."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.297 set value "You hear the footsteps too? Something walks unseen."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.298 set value "Your torch just flickered—run."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.299 set value "We do not say goodbye here—only good luck."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.300 set value "Build a treehouse above the canopy. I want to see the sky again."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.301 set value "I need a bridge across that river—the current swallowed our last one."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.302 set value "The temples were built by people who spoke to the trees. They are gone now."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.303 set value "Could you build a lookout tower? Something watches from the leaves."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.304 set value "An ancient people carved the mossy stone. The jungle ate them whole."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.305 set value "We need a proper dock—boats keep vanishing downstream."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.306 set value "Build me a raised hut. The ground breathes at night."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.307 set value "Whoever carved these idols knew things we have lost forever."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.308 set value "Make a shrine of mossy stone and glow berries. The jungle will approve."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.309 set value "A civilization once thrived here. Their artifacts sleep in the roots."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.310 set value "Put up tiki torches along the paths. Shadows swallow the unwary."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.311 set value "The old builders placed traps to guard something precious. Still active."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.312 set value "Build a ladder system through the trees. The ground is not safe."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.313 set value "Could you make a canopy walkway between the tall trees?"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.314 set value "There are engravings under the temple floor. Someone should see them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.315 set value "Build a cocoa farm platform on the big tree. Vines will guard it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.316 set value "The builders left poison in the temple walls. Respect that."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.317 set value "Make me a waterfall hideout. The noise hides everything."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.318 set value "Artifacts buried in roots pulse with old power. I feel them underfoot."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.319 set value "Could use lanterns on the jungle paths—things hunt in the dark."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.320 set value "Build a bonfire circle for storytelling. We must remember the old ways."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.321 set value "The temple architects understood redstone before redstone had a name."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.322 set value "We need a safe enclosure for our pandas—all seven of them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.323 set value "Can you make a hanging garden? Let the jungle claim it slowly."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.324 set value "The old civilization vanished in a single night. No one knows why."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.325 set value "Build a hidden tree vault for precious things. The vines will seal it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.326 set value "A watchtower would help spot what moves between the trunks at dusk."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.327 set value "Carve me a cave home behind the waterfall. Quiet and forgotten."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.328 set value "The mossy stone faces were not decorations. They were warnings."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.329 set value "Build a drum platform near the clearing. The jungle listens to rhythm."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.330 set value "Something sleeps beneath the largest temple. Best not to dig there."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.331 set value "I need a treetop sleeping pod—nothing reaches you up that high."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.332 set value "The original builders used vines as mortar. Stronger than anything we have."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.333 set value "Make a ceremonial fire ring. The old ones burned offerings here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.334 set value "Build benches near the cocoa trees. Even the doomed deserve rest."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.335 set value "Roots have swallowed entire villages before ours. We could be next."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.336 set value "Build an open-air library of jungle lore. Before we forget it all."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.337 set value "Can you plant a tree nursery? The old growth demands tribute."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.338 set value "The ancient people left maps carved into bark. We cannot read them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.339 set value "Put up banners to mark safe ground. Not all of it is."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.340 set value "Build a small stage for the parrots. They perform whether we want or not."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.341 set value "Could you restore that overgrown ruin? Treasures hide under the moss."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.342 set value "Make a treetop plaza—a place to breathe above the darkness below."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.343 set value "The ancient ones hid enchanting knowledge in temple alcoves."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.344 set value "Build a vine-covered tower. Something tall enough to pierce the canopy."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.345 set value "The civilization that built these temples also built the first Guidestones."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.346 set value "Make a meditation platform under the moonlight. Where dreams rise."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.347 set value "Build a stone archive. Someone should write down what the jungle whispers."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.348 set value "Dig out a storage cave beneath the roots. Cool and hidden from everything."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.jungle.349 set value "Surprise me—just make it mossy, mysterious, and touched by old magic."